  <description>
    <p>Aletheia is a cross-platform game save sync tool designed to help you easily back up and restore game saves across multiple game launchers and devices.</p>
    <p>Supported launchers include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Heroic Games</li>
      <li>Lutris</li>
      <li>Steam</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

